    "1302205": {
        "Desc": "Head into the heart of the research base",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "A sudden dizziness sets in, and a scene starts to play in your mind..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raju",
                    "T": "It's okay, Ilyas. You've done more than enough for me already..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "I don't understand. Everyone knows that Jani is stealing your research. Why is no one willing to go public with the truth?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "He shamelessly used your thesis to send in a project application, and whenever the project hits a wall, he asks you for help. Everyone knows what's going on..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raju",
                    "T": "Do you know how many people are working on that project? If Jani was kicked out because of academic fraud, that'd be the end of the project. Too many people would be affected!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "But he's obviously taking advantage of you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "He throws you the hardest work. After you're done pulling all-nighters, he struts around with your research data and takes credit for it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "That's not right! Why are you putting up with this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raju",
                    "T": "A lot of people warned me to not say anything, and I think they have a point. This is just how things are. All I want is to graduate without any problems..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raju",
                    "T": "It's okay. He's at least paying me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "Half a year of your time and effort, countless all-nighters, and casual threats and insults — all for a measly 20,000 Mora?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "He's treating people like cattle..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raju",
                    "T": "Enough. It's fine. I just need to suck it up and get it done."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "The scene ends there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's the matter?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I think I saw a glimpse of Ilyas's past."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh? You could read minds this whole time and you never told Paimon!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Of course not."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "I was also able to see those memories just now. They were probably the ones that leaked out while Ilyas was connecting to the collective consciousness."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Connecting? Collective consciousness?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "It's clear that this place isn't a work in progress. The Hive has long been finished."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "The collective consciousness project is already complete, and Ilyas is now returning to the collective."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So he tricked us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Not entirely... Keep walking and you'll see why."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1302208": {
        "Desc": "Listen to Ilyas's thoughts",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "The scene is much clearer this time, likely because it happened recently..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pitar",
                    "T": "Ilyas, this is all very strange. Is there really no research group that will take you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pitar",
                    "T": "To pass this course, you must complete a paper with other researchers. I know you're a hero for fighting academic fraud, but we can't make exceptions for heroes, now can we?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pitar",
                    "T": "Maybe you should try to improve your relationship with the other researchers. Getting a reputation for being too unconventional will not stand you in good stead in the long run."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "...I understand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Siraj",
                    "T": "You seem troubled."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "Who are you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Siraj",
                    "T": "Ah, where are my manners? My name is Siraj."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyas",
                    "T": "Siraj... I've heard of you before. Do you need something from me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Siraj",
                    "T": "The world hates people who don't fit in. I imagine you've had your fair share of trouble."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Siraj",
                    "T": "After you reported Jani for academic fraud, you were ostracized and shunned. Even your family can't understand your actions."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Siraj",
                    "T": "However, I'm working on some research that will help you \"merge into a collective.\" That way, your life won't be so dolorous."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Siraj",
                    "T": "How about it? Want to have a go?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "The scene ends there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "What did you see?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Siraj persuaded Ilyas to join the Hive."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Ilyas wasn't forced."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon can't believe it! He really did trick us, that giga jerk!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "No, Siraj is the real giga jerk here! Ilyas is just a regular jerk!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooh, Paimon's so mad! We're gonna find him, and we're gonna make him explain himself!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
